snippet.title: Faeland Square Enix Collective Trailer
snippet.description:
Faeland's Square Enix Collective campaign is now live (see link below). Your vote and feedback means a lot to us. We will also be showcasing our demo version in PAX East, April 5th-8th, Boston.
Faeland is coming to Kickstarter on April 17th!

https://collective.square-enix.com/projects/439/faeland

Visit Faeland's website to join us through the development!:
https://www.faelandgame.com

And our social media channels:
https://facebook.com/TaleGames
https://twitter.com/Talegamesnews
